snippet.title: Street Rod gameplay (PC Game, 1989)
snippet.description:
Introduction and gameplay for Street Rod, Dos PC game produced by California Dreams in 1989 - http://www.squakenet.com/download/street-rod/703/
Playing through a few different races in this old school driving game.
Played through Dosbox emulation platform.
Recorded with original sound.

Similar videos you may like:
Street Rod 2 - https://youtu.be/kDDKe0ukbVc
School Bus Driver - https://youtu.be/Qmw6HR9cFAs
Vette! - https://youtu.be/DrYjCSCQOYg
